The paper deals with the problem of designing a coordinated network dynamics for a group of agents under an observability constraint. This problem is relevant to several areas of computer science, including systems and control (cs.SY), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), robotics (cs.RO), distributed computing (cs.DC), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
